									<a href="https://lithub.com/tag/running-press/" title="Running Press" class="tag">Running Press</a>
							</div>

							<div class="bio-container">
					<div class="bio-img-container">
						<div class="bio-img">
							<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/NikkiVanDeCar_nocredit-copy-1-150x150.jpeg" width="96" height="96" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/NikkiVanDeCar_nocredit-copy-1-300x300.jpeg 2x" alt="Nikki Van De Car" class="avatar avatar-96 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-96 alignnone photo" />						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Nikki Van De Car</h4>
												<p>Nikki Van De Car is a blogger, mother, writer, crafter, and lover of all things mystical. She is the author of ten books on magic and crafting, including Practical Magic and The Junior Witch’s Handbook, and the founder of two popular knitting blogs. Nikki lives with her family in Hawaii.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			
